ift smaller than $\\pi/2$. With increase of\nvelocity, the structure evolves towards a rectangular configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2001 17:03:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
